<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ basics.name }} - Cover Letter</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: Letter;
            margin: 0.75in;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-color: #6A1B9A; /* Violet Highlight */
            --text-color: #333333;
            --light-text: #666666;
            --link-color: #7B1FA2;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-size: 10pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Header / Letterhead */
        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: var(--light-text);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            align-items: center;
            white-space: nowrap; /* prevent breaking email/links */
        }

        .contact-separator {
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--link-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            word-break: keep-all; /* avoid breaking addresses */
        }

        /* Letter Content */
        .meta-info {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .date {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .recipient {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .subject {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .signature-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ basics.name }}</h1>
        <div class="contact-info">
            {{ basics.location }}
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ basics.email }}">{{ basics.email }}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <a href="https://{{ basics.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="https://{{ basics.github }}">GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-info">
        <div class="date">{{ date }}</div>
        <div class="recipient">
            {{ recipient.name }}
            {% if recipient.title %}<br>{{ recipient.title }}{% endif %}
            {% if recipient.company %}<br>{{ recipient.company }}{% endif %}
            {% if recipient.address %}<br>{{ recipient.address }}{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="subject">{% if prospective_outreach %}Re: Exploring Opportunities in {{ role_title }}{% else %}Re: Application for {{ role_title }} Position{% endif %}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{ recipient.name }},</p>

        {% if prospective_outreach %}
        <p>I’m reaching out to express interest in upcoming opportunities at {{ recipient.company or 'your organization' }}. As a {{ basics.label }} and a PRS customer, I value your commitment to {{ company_focus or 'secure operations and environmental stewardship' }}. I’d welcome a brief conversation to explore where my background in forensic data handling and chain‑of‑custody could support your team.</p>
        {% else %}
        <p>I am writing to express my strong interest in the {{ role_title }} position. As a {{ basics.label }} with a background in {{ background_context }}, I am excited about the opportunity to contribute to your team's security posture.</p>
        {% endif %}

        <p>{{ summary }}</p>

        {% if program_eligibility is defined and program_eligibility.workbc_wage_subsidy_line %}
        <p>{{ program_eligibility.workbc_wage_subsidy_line }}</p>
        {% endif %}

        {% if summary_type == 'prs_canada' or company_focus %}
        <h3>Why {{ recipient.company or 'your company' }}?</h3>
        {% if summary_type == 'prs_canada' %}
        <p>Your company's commitment to {{ company_focus or 'secure operations and responsible technology practices' }} directly aligns with my experience in forensic data handling, {{ sanitization_standard }}‑aligned data‑wiping protocols, and chain‑of‑custody procedures. I value environmentally responsible asset remarketing and privacy‑first data practices, and I am eager to support these priorities.</p>

        <h3>How I Can Help</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Codify documented, auditable {{ sanitization_standard }}‑aligned sanitization SOPs and verification checklists.</li>
            <li>Tighten chain‑of‑custody logging with clearer handoff points and tamper‑evident documentation.</li>
            <li>Create simple client‑facing destruction/remarketing reports (before/after device state, certs, wipe IDs).</li>
            <li>Produce short privacy/sustainability explainer content for customers and partners.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Relevant Expertise</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Forensic Data Handling & Security Analysis:</strong> Experienced with {{ skills.security_tools[:3]|join(', ') }} and reporting practices that protect confidentiality and integrity.</li>
            <li><strong>Certified Data Wiping & Chain of Custody:</strong> Hands‑on work with verification, documentation, and lifecycle controls to ensure secure sanitization throughout asset handling.</li>
            {% if 'Shopify' in skills.programming %}
            <li><strong>Ecommerce/Web Security:</strong> Full‑stack experience ({{ (skills.programming|select('in', ['Node.js','React','PostgreSQL','Shopify'])|list)|join(', ') }}) with OWASP‑aligned secure coding, including SQL injection prevention and XSS protection.</li>
            {% endif %}
        </ul>
        {% elif summary_type == 'ymca_network_security' %}
        <p>YMCA BC's mission to strengthen community foundations through health equity and belonging resonates deeply with my commitment to security as an enabler—not a barrier—to organizational success. I'm drawn to your collaborative, mission-driven culture and excited to help safeguard the systems that support vital community services.</p>

        <h3>How I Can Contribute</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Monitor and maintain network infrastructure (firewalls, VPN, wireless, cloud) ensuring uptime and performance</li>
            <li>Proactively detect and respond to security incidents using SIEM tools and threat intelligence</li>
            <li>Perform regular vulnerability assessments and implement remediation strategies aligned with CIS/NIST frameworks</li>
            <li>Maintain clear documentation and communicate security findings to technical and non-technical stakeholders</li>
            <li>Support compliance initiatives (PCI-DSS, regulatory requirements) while enabling operational flexibility</li>
        </ul>
        {% else %}
        <p>Your company's commitment to {{ company_focus }} directly aligns with my experience in security operations, risk management, and building robust security controls.</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% endif %}

        <p>In my recent work, I have focused heavily on practical, hands-on security operations:</p>
        <ul>
            {% for project in projects[:2] %}
            <li>
                <strong>
                    {% if project.url %}
                    <a href="{{ project.url }}" target="_blank">{{ project.title }}</a>
                    {% else %}
                    {{ project.title }}
                    {% endif %}
                </strong>: {{ project.bullets[0] }}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>

        <p>My technical foundation in {{ skills.security_tools[:3]|join(', ') }} and {{ skills.programming[:2]|join(', ') }} allows me to bridge the gap between theoretical security concepts and real‑world implementation.</p>

        {% if prospective_outreach %}
        <p>If helpful, I’m available for a 15–20 minute chat this week or next. Thank you for your time—I’m excited about {{ recipient.company or 'your organization' }}’s mission and how I can contribute.</p>
        {% else %}
        <p>I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my skills and experience align with your needs. Thank you for your time and consideration.</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <div class="signature-name">{{ basics.name }}</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
